## Color Palette

### Backgrounds (layered elevation)

```
Base:       bg-[#0a0a0a] or bg-neutral-950
Surface 1:  bg-[#111111] or bg-neutral-900
Surface 2:  bg-[#171717] or bg-neutral-800
Elevated:   bg-[#1f1f1f] or bg-neutral-800/80
Overlay:    bg-black/50 (for modals, dropdowns)
```

### Sidebar

```
Background: bg-[#0d0d0d] or bg-neutral-950/95
Hover:      bg-white/5
Active:     bg-white/10
```

### Text

```
Primary:    text-white or text-neutral-50
Secondary:  text-neutral-400
Muted:      text-neutral-500
Disabled:   text-neutral-600
```

### Accent (use sparingly)

```
Primary:    violet-500 (#8b5cf6)
Hover:      violet-400
Active:     violet-600
Muted:      violet-500/20 (for backgrounds)
```

### Borders

```
Default:    border-white/10 or border-neutral-800
Subtle:     border-white/5
