## Typography

### Font Family

- Primary: `font-sans` (Inter)
- Headings: Use same family, differentiate with weight

### Weights

- Headings: `font-medium` or `font-semibold` (never `font-bold` except for strong emphasis)
- Body: `font-normal`
- Labels: `font-medium`

### Sizes

```
Page title:   text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight
Section:      text-lg font-medium
Body:         text-sm
Small/Label:  text-xs
Metadata:     text-xs text-neutral-500
```

### Tracking

- Headings: `tracking-tight`
- Body: default

---

## Spacing

### Padding Scale

```
Compact:    p-2, px-2 py-1
Default:    p-3, px-3 py-2
Comfortable: p-4, px-4 py-3
Spacious:   p-6
```

### Gaps

```
Tight:      gap-1, gap-2
Default:    gap-3, gap-4
Sections:   gap-6, gap-8
```

### Margins

- Use generous vertical spacing between sections
- Let content breathe — don't pack tightly

---

## Border Radius

**Critical: Linear uses minimal, sharp corners**

```
None:       rounded-none (for full-bleed elements)
Subtle:     rounded (4px) — default for most elements
Standard:   rounded-md (6px) — max for cards, containers
```

**Never use:**

- `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl` on UI elements
- `rounded-full` on containers (only for avatars, status dots)

