## Icons

- Size: `w-4 h-4` (16px) for inline, `w-5 h-5` (20px) for standalone
- Color: `text-neutral-400` default, `text-white` on hover/active
- Use consistent icon set (Lucide, Heroicons)
- Stroke width: 1.5-2px

---

## Focus States

All interactive elements must have visible focus:

```
focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-violet-500/50 focus:border-violet-500
```

Or for elements without borders:

```
focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-500/50 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-900
```

