## Anti-Patterns (AVOID)

### Colors

- ❌ Gradient backgrounds (`bg-gradient-to-*`) except for branded elements like logos
- ❌ Multiple accent colors in the same view
- ❌ Pure black (`bg-black`) as primary background
- ❌ Bright/saturated colors for large surfaces

### Radius

- ❌ `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl` on UI containers
- ❌ `rounded-full` on buttons, cards, containers

### Typography

- ❌ `font-bold` in body text (use `font-medium` or `font-semibold`)
- ❌ ALL CAPS for body text (only for tiny labels if at all)
- ❌ Decorative fonts

### Effects

- ❌ Heavy drop shadows
- ❌ Glowing/neon effects
- ❌ Blur effects on primary content
- ❌ Animations longer than 300ms
- ❌ Bounce/elastic easings

### Layout

- ❌ Cramped spacing
- ❌ Excessive visual separators
- ❌ Decorative dividers

---

## Dark Mode Only Considerations

Since this system is dark-mode-first:

- Test contrast ratios for accessibility (WCAG AA minimum)
- Ensure text remains readable on all surface levels
- Use opacity-based colors for consistency across themes
- Primary text should be `text-white` not a gray

