## Checklist for Component Audit

When refactoring existing components, verify:

- [ ] Background uses neutral-900/950, not black or grays outside palette
- [ ] Borders use `border-white/10` or `border-neutral-800`
- [ ] Border radius is `rounded` or `rounded-md` max
- [ ] Text uses correct hierarchy (white → neutral-400 → neutral-500)
- [ ] Accent color is violet, used only for interactive states
- [ ] Transitions are 150-200ms, colors only
- [ ] No gradient backgrounds (except branded elements)
- [ ] Focus states are visible and use violet ring
- [ ] Hover states use opacity shifts (`bg-white/5`, `bg-white/10`)
- [ ] Icons are 16-20px, neutral-400 default color
- [ ] Font weights are normal/medium/semibold (no bold)
